{"id":563476,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/07/【立此存照】只许州官放火：微博及评论内容中禁/","date":"2017-07-11T07:08:09Z","modified":"2017-10-06T21:56:27Z","title":"【立此存照】只许州官放火：微博及评论中禁止出现“郭文贵”","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>中国官方突然高调反击郭文贵的爆料指控。新华社近日接连发表有关<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/07/%e6%96%b0%e6%b5%aa%e8%b4%a2%e7%bb%8f-%e6%96%b0%e5%8d%8e%e7%a4%be%e6%b7%b1%e5%a4%9c%e5%88%8a%e6%96%87%ef%bc%9a%e6%b5%b7%e8%88%aa%e8%a2%ab%e7%88%86%e6%96%99%e7%9c%9f%e7%9b%b8/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">郭文贵“海航‘爆料’真相调查”</a>、回国心切“<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/07/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e9%83%ad%e8%af%b4%e7%9a%84%e6%98%af%e7%9c%9f%e7%9a%84%e5%90%97%ef%bc%9f%e6%8d%ae%e8%af%b4%e8%bf%98%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%9c%e5%86%b0%e5%86%b0%ef%bc%9f/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">被骗2000万元始末</a>”的报道，相关内容甚至出现在了央视《新闻直播间》节目。这是郭文贵开始爆料以来，官方第一次就其具体爆料内容——王岐山外甥姚庆用海航集团资金为自己定制波音787私人飞机——进行反驳。</p>\n<p><strong>然而与官媒的高调回应相比，中国普通网民却连在微博发表含有“郭文贵”或“GWG”的内容，都不被允许：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-563477\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG1.jpg 1330w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG1-300x190.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG1-768x486.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG1-1024x648.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/gwg2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-563484\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/gwg2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/gwg2.jpg 1334w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/gwg2-300x190.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/gwg2-768x486.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/gwg2-1024x648.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>含有“郭文贵”的微博评论也无法发表：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-563485\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG3.jpg 1356w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG3-300x181.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG3-768x463.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG3-1024x618.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/GWG3-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[13232,8585,32692,23589,8859,33354,32696,9166,14693,26519,32686]}